data.name: StringTable.Message_ToProceed
data.value:
To Proceed with the cylinder cutout test: • Turn off the Air Conditioner and the Defrost • Lock the cooling fan ON by either disconnecting the fan control solenoid OR by using the dash overide switch.
Note that if fan solenoid is disconnected all fault codes need to be cleared after reconnecting the fan solenoid
